abstract = {Mobile peer-to-peer (MP2P) services are currently emerging due to the growing experimentation in both the academia and the industry. This paper presents the initial results of a scenario analysis applied to MP2P services. We also discuss the scenario methodology in general. We have possibly identified the most significant uncertainties related to MP2P services and the most essential trends behind the uncertainties. We conclude by presenting initial scenarios. Our future aim is to complete a full scenario analysis on MP2P based on the results presented in this paper.},
